  "title": "Account cum Admin Assistant (Partial Set) - 5days | Paya Lebar",
  "description": "<p><strong> Account cum Admin Assistant</strong><br />Salary : $2500-$3000 (Depends on exp)<br />Working Days: 5-day work week (9.00am to 6.00pm)<br />Location : PAYA LEBAR ROAD<br /><br /><u><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></u></p><p>• Monitor day-to-day company account activities</p><p>• Update debtors’ ledger and record accounts payable and receivable</p><p>• Prepare and send summaries of aged receivables and monitor timely customer payments</p><p>• Prepare payments to vendors</p><p>• File and mail/courier invoices and documents prepared by the operations team</p><p>• Monitor AGM and Annual Return dates for each company</p><p>• Prepare Financial Statements (Balance Sheet, P&L, Tax Computations, etc.) and liaise with the company secretary for submission</p><p>• Prepare and submit monthly CPF contributions</p><p>• Prepare and submit IR8A annually</p><p>• Handle daily accounts and administrative work, including ad-hoc duties assigned by Managers / Directors</p><p><strong>Tee Xin Li Reg No: R24121619</strong><br /><strong>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
